data.text:
Sankho, a multifaceted artist with expertise in music, singing, direction, and film-making, has embarked on a new venture, with the aim of sharing his knowledge and experience with a wider audience, has launched a platform, VIPOP SHOW .

Under the banner of VIPOP SHOW PVT LIMITED, Sankho brings his extensive experience and creativity to the world of learning Music & Films for the learners of different age groups and different socio-economic backgrounds.

At VIPOP SHOW, we are committed to providing the highest quality online courses and consultations that are tailored to the needs of our clients.
